<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<style>
body { 
  font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif; 
  line-height: 1.6; 
  color: #333; 
  background-color: #f5f5f5; 
  margin: 0; 
  padding: 20px; 
}
.container { 
  max-width: 600px; 
  margin: 0 auto; 
  background-color: #ffffff; 
  padding: 30px; 
  border-radius: 8px;
  box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
}
.header {
  margin-bottom: 20px;
  text-align: center;
}
.header h1 {
  color: #4a90e2;
  font-size: 24px;
  margin: 0 0 10px 0;
}
.content p { 
  margin: 10px 0; 
  color: #555; 
  text-align: center;
}
.code {
  font-size: 36px;
  font-weight: bold;
  color: #4a90e2;
  letter-spacing: 6px;
  text-align: center;
  padding: 25px;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9fa 0%, #e9ecef 100%);
  border: 2px dashed #4a90e2;
  border-radius: 8px;
  margin: 25px 0;
  font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
}
.warning {
  color: #e74c3c;
  font-size: 14px;
  text-align: center;
  margin-top: 15px;
  font-weight: 500;
}
.info {
  color: #7f8c8d;
  font-size: 14px;
  text-align: center;
  margin-top: 10px;
}
.footer { 
  margin-top: 30px; 
  padding-top: 20px; 
  border-top: 1px solid #eee; 
  text-align: center; 
  color: #999; 
  font-size: 13px; 
}
.footer a { 
  color: #4a90e2; 
  text-decoration: none; 
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
  <div class="header">
    <h1>🔒 重置密码</h1>
  </div>
  <div class="content">
    <p>您正在重置 <strong>{{.SiteName}}</strong> 的密码</p>
    <p>您的验证码是：</p>
    <div class="code">{{.Code}}</div>
    <p class="info">验证码有效期为 30 分钟，请及时使用</p>
    <p class="warning">⚠️ 如非本人操作，请立即修改密码！</p>
  </div>
  <div class="footer">
    <p>此邮件由 {{.SiteName}} 自动发送，请勿直接回复</p>
    <p><a href="{{.SiteURL}}">访问网站</a></p>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
